description: [AAI] The Africa-America Institute (AAI) marked a significant milestone on Tuesday, September 24th, with its 40th Annual Awards Gala. The prestigious event, held in New York City, brought together an impressive array of distinguished leaders from Africa, across the diaspora, and the United States to celebrate achievements in African leadership and philanthropy.
title: Africa: AAI Celebrates 40th Annual Awards Gala Honoring African Leadership and Philanthropy
